\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%91%A8%E6%A2%93%E6%A8%82%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-9-%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E7%AB%8B%E5%A0%B4-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA%E9%81%AD%E6%88%AA%E6%9F%A5-%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%87%B4%E9%9B%BB%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%A5%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E5%B1%AC%E5%8F%97%E8%96%AA%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5/</a><br />\n<br />\n今日（8 日）是科大學生周梓樂去世 9 個月，《立場新聞》一名攝影記者在將軍澳採訪市民悼念行動期間，與另外兩名記者一同被警員截查。《立場》記者當時身穿反光衣，出示記者證和身份證後，仍被警員要求證明是「受薪員工」，最後更指示記者致電同事以證明身份。兩名同行記者最終被發限聚令告票，警員稱二人不是記者，「你哋行埋一齊呢，違反咗限聚令，淨係告佢哋兩個，因為佢兩個唔係記者，唔係度做嘢。」《立場》正就警方要求記者工作時出示「受薪證明」一事，向警方查詢準則和根據。"},{"pid":"c3e795cfbc2ba18be0dd48dab66b4fcf775ce036","tid":2146540,"uid":172823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b09d7671a6b13401cf0be3c1f72b7d0d4ac01a","tid":2146540,"uid":188176,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:55:11.000Z","msg":"根據基本法,無論係唔係受薪都可以係記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過同恐怖分子講法律都無乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2b24de690cc6581d8f8e2cbc4775e63479767f","tid":2146540,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f7b0d0bb32c6f6a0f5440d6ba4394655d5896c","tid":2146540,"uid":160373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:55:23.000Z","msg":"黑狗都有機會入埋制裁名單<br />\nMON PO狗你開咗崑崙銀行戶口未"},{"pid":"ee0ebb5f5953822316588fd407